Comment: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:01.00,Default,,0,0,0,,======================================== TEXT ========================================
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.64,0:00:12.59,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么办啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.96,0:00:16.62,Default,,0,0,0,,那个 菜子
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.22,0:00:19.96,Default,,0,0,0,,我生气了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.66,0:00:28.44,Default,,0,0,0,,香依
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.81,0:00:31.84,Default,,0,0,0,,我又没有朋友了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.70,0:00:37.23,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么办怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.51,0:00:38.76,Default,,0,0,0,,要去道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.69,0:00:41.33,Default,,0,0,0,,但是要怎么做
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.36,0:00:44.46,Default,,0,0,0,,对了 手机查一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.97,0:00:46.39,Default,,0,0,0,,谢罪的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.74,0:00:49.62,Default,,0,0,0,,穿着正式 带上点心盒
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.08,0:00:51.72,Default,,0,0,0,,诚心诚意道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.47,0:00:54.31,Default,,0,0,0,,正式的服装是什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.68,0:00:56.35,Default,,0,0,0,,我只有体操服呀
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.55,0:00:58.64,Default,,0,0,0,,要怎么做
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.48,0:01:00.50,Default,,0,0,0,,一里同学？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.50,0:01:02.97,Default,,0,0,0,,人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.33,0:01:06.75,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么啦 不舒服吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.37,0:01:10.48,Default,,0,0,0,,被搭话了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.06,0:01:15.49,Default,,0,0,0,,不 现在不是这种时候
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.03,0:01:18.47,Default,,0,0,0,,第一次跟你说话呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.92,0:01:21.02,Default,,0,0,0,,我跟你是一个班的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.02,0:01:22.13,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.76,0:01:26.73,Default,,0,0,0,,本庄同学
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.73,0:01:31.65,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\an1\fn@方正粗圆_GBK\frz-90\c&H1A1F28&\fad(500,0)\pos(358.148,524.423)}本庄阿鲁
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.28,0:01:29.19,Default,,0,0,0,,是的 我叫本庄阿鲁
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.41,0:01:30.19,Default,,0,0,0,,请多关照哦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.64,0:01:31.69,Default,,0,0,0,,给你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.28,0:01:39.66,Default,,0,0,0,,非常感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.82,0:01:40.78,Default,,0,0,0,,没事
Comment: 0,0:01:44.97,0:01:46.82,Default,,0,0,0,,=======OP=======
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.09,0:03:19.67,Title,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)\c&HA66EF1&\pos(1782.412,803.769)}其实{\fs40\c&H9FA144&}是{\r\c&HA66EF1&}谢谢你的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.78,0:03:20.46,Default,,0,0,0,,这样啊 让砂尾同学生气了呀
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.71,0:03:23.60,Default,,0,0,0,,那真是头疼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.16,0:03:26.82,Default,,0,0,0,,本庄同学人太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.93,0:03:29.76,Default,,0,0,0,,话说回来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.28,0:03:32.15,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么那么警惕我呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.58,0:03:35.13,Default,,0,0,0,,这是尊敬
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.37,0:03:36.41,Default,,0,0,0,,老样子了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.09,0:03:39.04,Default,,0,0,0,,算了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.55,0:03:43.24,Default,,0,0,0,,那我就来给你帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.42,0:03:48.28,Default,,0,0,0,,解决班上的问题也是副班长的职责
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.68,0:03:49.74,Default,,0,0,0,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.70,0:03:53.80,Default,,0,0,0,,我只有体操服
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.80,0:03:54.24,Default,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.94,0:03:56.35,Default,,0,0,0,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.40,0:04:05.66,Default,,0,0,0,,菜子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.31,0:04:10.20,Default,,0,0,0,,不要哭了 去和她好好讲清楚吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.46,0:04:11.96,Default,,0,0,0,,是怎么让她生气的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.23,0:04:14.27,Default,,0,0,0,,是为什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.70,0:04:15.81,Default,,0,0,0,,你不知道的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.33,0:04:18.12,Default,,0,0,0,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.36,0:04:21.58,Default,,0,0,0,,那就先说说一开始发生了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.01,0:04:24.03,Default,,0,0,0,,一开始是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.66,0:04:29.74,Default,,0,0,0,,海带和裙带菜的区别是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.78,0:04:30.89,Default,,0,0,0,,是口感
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.26,0:04:32.55,Default,,0,0,0,,分享烦恼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.24,0:04:36.77,Default,,0,0,0,,有一样的烦恼的话 就一定能搞好关系
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.36,0:04:39.71,Default,,0,0,0,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.28,0:04:43.14,Default,,0,0,0,,这样就能跟菜子关系更好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.34,0:04:50.08,Default,,0,0,0,,等着我 菜子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.33,0:04:52.65,Default,,0,0,0,,我觉得可以
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.29,0:04:58.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Cock-a-doodle-doo-ooo我觉得不行
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.78,0:05:00.78,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.57,0:05:04.66,Default,,0,0,0,,还是不行 是我得意了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.89,0:05:07.11,Default,,0,0,0,,没法一上来问烦恼的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.19,0:05:09.09,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么呀
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.45,0:05:12.11,Default,,0,0,0,,我晚上就会觉得什么都能行
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.56,0:05:13.28,Default,,0,0,0,,所以
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.29,0:05:16.73,Default,,0,0,0,,波知 早啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.77,0:05:19.29,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.12,0:05:22.34,Default,,0,0,0,,晚上的我很厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.59,0:05:24.46,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎么突然说这个
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.20,0:05:28.26,Default,,0,0,0,,波知
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.62,0:05:31.38,Default,,0,0,0,,一起在学校里探险吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.66,0:05:34.92,Default,,0,0,0,,入学还没去过的地方还有很多的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.90,0:05:38.55,Default,,0,0,0,,和菜子学校探险…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.63,0:05:40.73,Default,,0,0,0,,和菜子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.08,0:05:44.25,Default,,0,0,0,,想去的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.05,0:05:49.72,Default,,0,0,0,,然后两个人休息的时候就在校舍里探险
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.57,0:05:53.59,Default,,0,0,0,,还以为菜子是不喜欢到处走的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.13,0:05:55.60,Default,,0,0,0,,你好过分啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.64,0:05:59.07,Default,,0,0,0,,事实上是这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.37,0:06:02.22,Default,,0,0,0,,不过今天是特别的 可是探险呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.61,0:06:03.23,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.14,0:06:06.84,Default,,0,0,0,,你手上拿的是什么呀
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.79,0:06:10.15,Default,,0,0,0,,说到探险 就是笛子了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.35,0:06:11.00,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.14,0:06:13.75,Default,,0,0,0,,随便走走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.40,0:06:16.37,Default,,0,0,0,,往上还是往下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.06,0:06:18.28,Default,,0,0,0,,你来决定吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.62,0:06:19.95,Default,,0,0,0,,这个
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.74,0:06:22.90,Default,,0,0,0,,那下面吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.07,0:06:36.75,Default,,0,0,0,,波知 要丢下你咯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.36,0:06:44.29,Default,,0,0,0,,波知
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.85,0:06:45.79,Default,,0,0,0,,来了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.92,0:06:47.93,Default,,0,0,0,,是小卖部
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.11,0:06:49.42,Default,,0,0,0,,关着呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.72,0:06:52.34,Default,,0,0,0,,中午好像卖面包的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.86,0:06:54.09,Default,,0,0,0,,下次来买买看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.55,0:06:55.00,Default,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.22,0:07:03.85,Default,,0,0,0,,可疑的厕所呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.88,0:07:05.15,Default,,0,0,0,,可疑的厕所
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.63,0:07:07.22,Default,,0,0,0,,真可疑呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.50,0:07:09.47,Default,,0,0,0,,感觉有点什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.67,0:07:17.77,Default,,0,0,0,,有东西在
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.77,0:07:18.62,Default,,0,0,0,,真可疑
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.75,0:07:20.46,Default,,0,0,0,,是的 我去看看
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.95,0:07:32.44,Default,,0,0,0,,什么都没有
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.93,0:07:34.10,Default,,0,0,0,,你不害怕吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.57,0:07:37.96,Default,,0,0,0,,我很少被搭话的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.11,0:07:40.46,Default,,0,0,0,,觉得能交朋友就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.96,0:07:41.68,Default,,0,0,0,,哭了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.30,0:07:46.10,Default,,0,0,0,,镜子？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.36,0:07:47.72,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么有全身镜
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.43,0:07:51.26,Default,,0,0,0,,波知裙子那么长不好看呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.54,0:07:53.38,Default,,0,0,0,,不好看的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.64,0:07:55.25,Default,,0,0,0,,不行的呀
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.90,0:07:57.21,Default,,0,0,0,,那要怎么做呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.52,0:08:01.36,Default,,0,0,0,,是时候探险结束了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.59,0:08:02.25,Default,,0,0,0,,已经要结束了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.62,0:08:07.07,Default,,0,0,0,,这次是在做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.65,0:08:10.19,Default,,0,0,0,,然后就到了下午的课
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.20,0:08:12.21,Default,,0,0,0,,还有继续的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.72,0:08:13.78,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.11,0:08:15.77,Default,,0,0,0,,没事 然后呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.62,0:08:28.36,Default,,0,0,0,,这是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.68,0:08:32.34,Default,,0,0,0,,上课时候想说话的时候传过来的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.46,0:08:33.67,Default,,0,0,0,,信一样的那个
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.12,0:08:35.37,Default,,0,0,0,,向往很久的那个
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.20,0:08:39.47,Default,,0,0,0,,当做宝物吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.53,0:08:43.00,Default,,0,0,0,,你看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.40,0:08:48.17,Default,,0,0,0,,接下来去屋顶
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.42,0:08:49.10,Default,,0,0,0,,羊驼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.86,0:08:52.16,Default,,0,0,0,,回信回信
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.32,0:09:08.42,Default,,0,0,0,,羊驼特征是全身软软的毛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.52,0:09:09.99,Default,,0,0,0,,但是是骆驼科的动物
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.47,0:09:11.40,Default,,0,0,0,,回的这个？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.88,0:09:15.10,Default,,0,0,0,,然后两个人放学来到了屋顶
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.19,0:09:21.29,Default,,0,0,0,,好漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.54,0:09:22.79,Default,,0,0,0,,来了真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.06,0:09:23.54,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.81,0:09:28.53,Default,,0,0,0,,没事吧 都变红了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.98,0:09:35.55,Default,,0,0,0,,被和菜子搞好关系的书砸到了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.02,0:09:37.18,Default,,0,0,0,,那什么书啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.90,0:09:40.50,Default,,0,0,0,,现在还带着
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.87,0:09:46.67,Default,,0,0,0,,原来如此 分享烦恼嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.96,0:09:47.51,Default,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.86,0:09:51.05,Default,,0,0,0,,那波知有什么想要告诉我的烦恼吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.53,0:09:52.33,Default,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.83,0:09:54.21,Default,,0,0,0,,我的烦恼是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.20,0:09:58.58,Default,,0,0,0,,不知道怎么问菜子的烦恼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.59,0:09:59.69,Default,,0,0,0,,很烦恼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.99,0:10:00.85,Default,,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.38,0:10:02.65,Default,,0,0,0,,那太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.75,0:10:04.78,Default,,0,0,0,,已经解决了 现在
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.67,0:10:15.14,Default,,0,0,0,,我还没有解决
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.21,0:10:16.15,Default,,0,0,0,,别哭啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.75,0:10:20.97,Default,,0,0,0,,那菜子的烦恼是？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.29,0:10:22.98,Default,,0,0,0,,我的烦恼嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.27,0:10:23.74,Default,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.46,0:10:33.03,Default,,0,0,0,,入学以来就被奇怪的家伙跟着 这个吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.56,0:10:35.74,Default,,0,0,0,,奇怪的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.47,0:10:39.52,Default,,0,0,0,,突然说想做朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.12,0:10:41.98,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然不知道想要干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.15,0:10:43.88,Default,,0,0,0,,但很有行动力
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.70,0:10:46.53,Default,,0,0,0,,不过嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.04,0:10:49.38,Default,,0,0,0,,还挺开心的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.78,0:10:58.56,Default,,0,0,0,,菜子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.90,0:11:03.50,Default,,0,0,0,,我也能和那个人做朋友吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.60,0:11:04.15,Default,,0,0,0,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.36,0:11:06.85,Default,,0,0,0,,在哪呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.22,0:11:17.98,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.77,0:11:21.98,Default,,0,0,0,,难道说缠着菜子的是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.60,0:11:26.56,Default,,0,0,0,,能和我交朋友吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.99,0:11:31.11,Default,,0,0,0,,然后那天还好好的回家的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.55,0:11:32.75,Default,,0,0,0,,然后今天
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.98,0:11:36.20,Default,,0,0,0,,和全班都做朋友？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.62,0:11:37.00,Default,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.63,0:11:38.62,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么又
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.93,0:11:40.52,Default,,0,0,0,,和小时候的伙伴 香依
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.16,0:11:43.50,Default,,0,0,0,,和朋友约定的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.13,0:11:47.68,Default,,0,0,0,,没有和全班交朋友就绝交
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.33,0:11:49.05,Default,,0,0,0,,全员
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.72,0:11:50.17,Default,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.69,0:11:54.11,Default,,0,0,0,,香依是为了我好才这么说的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.87,0:11:58.11,Default,,0,0,0,,就是说
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.45,0:12:03.02,Default,,0,0,0,,一开始跟我搭话 也是因为和她的约定是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.47,0:12:03.97,Default,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.56,0:12:06.73,Default,,0,0,0,,是嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.18,0:12:08.25,Default,,0,0,0,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.08,0:12:11.53,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么办啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.10,0:12:15.54,Default,,0,0,0,,菜子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.94,0:12:18.71,Default,,0,0,0,,我生气了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.62,0:12:22.00,Default,,0,0,0,,引子好长
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.00,0:12:24.51,Default,,0,0,0,,然后就不跟我说话了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.91,0:12:27.69,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么想原因都是这个吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.48,0:12:32.19,Default,,0,0,0,,本庄同学 为什么在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.77,0:12:34.03,Default,,0,0,0,,你没察觉到吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.58,0:12:37.77,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知何时说了很多
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.21,0:12:39.75,Default,,0,0,0,,不用管那些的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.93,0:12:43.42,Default,,0,0,0,,走吧 交给副班长我吧
Comment: 0,0:12:43.60,0:12:46.58,Default,,0,0,0,,===============
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.00,0:12:48.83,Default,,0,0,0,,菜子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.90,0:12:51.53,Default,,0,0,0,,第一次说的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.80,0:12:52.89,Default,,0,0,0,,发的消息
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.15,0:12:54.40,Default,,0,0,0,,探险的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.01,0:12:57.03,Default,,0,0,0,,就像是很久以前的事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.49,0:13:00.58,Default,,0,0,0,,事实上只过了几天而已
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.38,0:13:02.30,Default,,0,0,0,,话说回来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.43,0:13:03.19,Default,,0,0,0,,一里同学
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.79,0:13:04.94,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么换衣服了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.74,0:13:07.23,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么会生气呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.00,0:13:09.35,Default,,0,0,0,,就算不去道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.78,0:13:13.84,Default,,0,0,0,,好好表达现在自己的心意她一定能理解你的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.27,0:13:14.99,Default,,0,0,0,,心意？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.66,0:13:18.55,Default,,0,0,0,,是的 想到的全部都
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.13,0:13:19.80,Default,,0,0,0,,全部
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.04,0:13:23.62,Default,,0,0,0,,去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.78,0:13:35.61,Default,,0,0,0,,全部全部全部…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.85,0:13:39.97,Default,,0,0,0,,脚抽筋了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.81,0:13:42.06,Default,,0,0,0,,感觉既视感
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.44,0:13:48.17,Default,,0,0,0,,一开始觉得菜子有些可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.65,0:13:50.56,Default,,0,0,0,,但是很温柔
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.25,0:13:54.49,Default,,0,0,0,,因为和香依约好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.89,0:13:56.48,Default,,0,0,0,,才能够去搭话
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.40,0:14:00.72,Default,,0,0,0,,因为约定 才对菜子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.09,0:14:02.69,Default,,0,0,0,,能喜欢上菜子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.19,0:14:06.68,Default,,0,0,0,,笨蛋 要被误会的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.84,0:14:08.45,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么是体操服啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.80,0:14:09.69,Default,,0,0,0,,然后就
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.92,0:14:12.89,DefaultTop,,0,0,0,,休息的时候和菜子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.22,0:14:15.31,DefaultTop,,0,0,0,,在校内探险
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.55,0:14:17.21,DefaultTop,,0,0,0,,问我上面还是下面
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.22,0:14:15.22,Default,,0,0,0,,看来没问题了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.74,0:14:17.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我就失陪了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.50,0:14:18.95,Default,,0,0,0,,打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.01,0:14:20.23,Default,,0,0,0,,误会还…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.68,0:14:24.06,DefaultTop,,0,0,0,,然后突然发现可疑的厕所
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.67,0:14:24.60,Default,,0,0,0,,这边还在继续
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.29,0:14:27.89,DefaultTop,,0,0,0,,我吹笛子进了厕所
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.22,0:14:26.07,Default,,0,0,0,,波知
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.19,0:14:29.08,Default,,0,0,0,,波知
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.96,0:14:31.21,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.76,0:14:33.21,Default,,0,0,0,,不生气了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.88,0:14:34.74,Default,,0,0,0,,菜子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.69,0:14:37.34,Default,,0,0,0,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.78,0:14:38.64,Default,,0,0,0,,真的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.62,0:14:41.59,Default,,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.60,0:14:43.19,Default,,0,0,0,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.64,0:14:46.62,Default,,0,0,0,,那为什么生气的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.76,0:14:48.42,Default,,0,0,0,,你还是不懂的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.42,0:14:51.14,Default,,0,0,0,,说了的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.68,0:14:54.65,Default,,0,0,0,,你说想做朋友我很高兴的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.16,0:14:56.06,Default,,0,0,0,,菜子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.76,0:15:01.99,Default,,0,0,0,,你说谁都可以的话 我就很震惊了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.36,0:15:05.43,Default,,0,0,0,,不是谁都可以的 因为是菜子才
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.58,0:15:07.02,Default,,0,0,0,,那是后面加的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.18,0:15:09.35,Default,,0,0,0,,一开始是其他动机的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.47,0:15:11.96,Default,,0,0,0,,一开始是因为你坐在前面
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.61,0:15:14.53,Default,,0,0,0,,所以说震惊这个
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.92,0:15:16.38,Default,,0,0,0,,算了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.36,0:15:18.46,Default,,0,0,0,,话说回来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.68,0:15:20.28,Default,,0,0,0,,全员都交朋友嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.72,0:15:21.83,Default,,0,0,0,,没问题吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.27,0:15:24.10,Default,,0,0,0,,不知道 但是我会加油的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.42,0:15:26.83,Default,,0,0,0,,不是敬语了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.41,0:15:29.16,Default,,0,0,0,,加油吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.33,0:15:31.32,Default,,0,0,0,,是的 我会加油的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.35,0:15:33.30,Default,,0,0,0,,不要变回敬语啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.24,0:15:37.75,Default,,0,0,0,,不过那个叫香依的 约定的也真奇怪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.23,0:15:39.30,Default,,0,0,0,,约定
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.08,0:15:43.78,Default,,0,0,0,,波知 当了地主要让我住住哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.02,0:15:47.20,Default,,0,0,0,,这是什么约定啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.49,0:15:50.72,Default,,0,0,0,,你有头绪吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.24,0:15:53.60,Default,,0,0,0,,其他有谁能做朋友的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.05,0:15:55.10,Default,,0,0,0,,这个
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.47,0:15:57.35,Default,,0,0,0,,放弃思考了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.66,0:16:02.36,Default,,0,0,0,,不过 今天跟我搭话的那个人的话应该
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.73,0:16:05.04,Default,,0,0,0,,应该不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.22,0:16:06.06,Default,,0,0,0,,你上啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.68,0:16:09.58,Default,,0,0,0,,菜子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.37,0:16:11.13,Default,,0,0,0,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.66,0:16:13.32,Default,,0,0,0,,波知 早啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.91,0:16:16.35,Default,,0,0,0,,能正常打招呼了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.82,0:16:19.21,Default,,0,0,0,,准备好去搭话了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.48,0:16:23.13,Default,,0,0,0,,别吐啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.01,0:16:27.86,Default,,0,0,0,,不过你居然能第一天和我搭话呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.28,0:16:31.06,Default,,0,0,0,,那是菜子先跟我说话的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.53,0:16:32.78,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了 呕吐妹
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.50,0:16:35.12,Default,,0,0,0,,那你也能高兴的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.27,0:16:38.93,Default,,0,0,0,,那被搭话了是什么情况
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.41,0:16:40.27,Default,,0,0,0,,本庄同学
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.51,0:16:43.71,Default,,0,0,0,,和菜子和好的时候给我帮忙了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.08,0:16:45.34,Default,,0,0,0,,好体贴的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.60,0:16:48.51,Default,,0,0,0,,那个笑容很虚假的孩子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.12,0:16:52.49,Default,,0,0,0,,听见在谈论我了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.82,0:16:54.22,Default,,0,0,0,,出现了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.57,0:16:58.19,Default,,0,0,0,,和砂尾同学和好了真是太好了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.21,0:17:00.32,Default,,0,0,0,,谢…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.69,0:17:02.59,Default,,0,0,0,,谢了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.07,0:17:03.75,Default,,0,0,0,,谢了？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.11,0:17:07.45,Default,,0,0,0,,体育系的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.76,0:17:08.32,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.81,0:17:11.70,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么还有衣架
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.31,0:17:13.24,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.61,0:17:14.81,Default,,0,0,0,,没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.08,0:17:15.84,Default,,0,0,0,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.71,0:17:17.26,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.65,0:17:19.50,Default,,0,0,0,,你衣架在身上
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.39,0:17:25.12,Default,,0,0,0,,这是早上比较赶
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.12,0:17:27.38,Default,,0,0,0,,不是的 我不会迟到的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.44,0:17:28.67,Default,,0,0,0,,平时时间都充足的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.69,0:17:30.39,Default,,0,0,0,,所以说
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.50,0:17:31.70,Default,,0,0,0,,这是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.07,0:17:33.74,Default,,0,0,0,,潮流
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.66,0:17:36.35,Default,,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.62,0:17:38.52,Default,,0,0,0,,就是潮流
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.59,0:17:41.21,Default,,0,0,0,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.70,0:17:42.60,Default,,0,0,0,,安全
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.84,0:17:44.04,Default,,0,0,0,,不不不
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.10,0:17:48.13,Default,,0,0,0,,我说怎么感觉是伪装的笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.44,0:17:49.27,Default,,0,0,0,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.42,0:17:51.46,Default,,0,0,0,,你是残念的孩子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.99,0:17:54.35,Default,,0,0,0,,残念？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.82,0:17:57.47,Default,,0,0,0,,比如说早上走得很急的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.73,0:17:59.46,Default,,0,0,0,,忘记穿内裤啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.12,0:18:04.90,Default,,0,0,0,,不会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.11,0:18:06.95,Default,,0,0,0,,这是妈妈的内裤
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.03,0:18:07.93,Default,,0,0,0,,不会的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.40,0:18:12.69,Default,,0,0,0,,不是的呀 这是和妈妈一套的内裤
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.77,0:18:14.62,Default,,0,0,0,,不 这也够残念了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.25,0:18:19.29,Default,,0,0,0,,不是的 爷爷老家的习俗有这种的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.29,0:18:20.34,Default,,0,0,0,,够残念了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.49,0:18:23.20,Default,,0,0,0,,俗话说得好 母亲的内裤…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.20,0:18:23.83,Default,,0,0,0,,残念
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.73,0:18:30.60,Default,,0,0,0,,什么嘛 什么呀
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.80,0:18:32.24,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么暴露了呀
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.64,0:18:34.07,Default,,0,0,0,,我真是傻瓜
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.91,0:18:37.98,Default,,0,0,0,,我真是傻瓜
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.03,0:18:38.58,Default,,0,0,0,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.23,0:18:41.43,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.03,0:18:46.63,Default,,0,0,0,,菜子 怎么办啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.80,0:18:48.58,Default,,0,0,0,,本庄同学生气了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.78,0:18:51.30,Default,,0,0,0,,这样啊 做了多余的事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.81,0:18:54.62,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉 以为她不是好人就
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.54,0:18:58.75,Default,,0,0,0,,波知比较容易被骗吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.23,0:19:04.06,Default,,0,0,0,,不过 看来不是坏家伙呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.13,0:19:10.32,Default,,0,0,0,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.91,0:19:13.46,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了 来笑我了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.86,0:19:19.88,Default,,0,0,0,,没错 我出生到现在一直都被说是残念的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.64,0:19:23.36,Default,,0,0,0,,所以到了初中想要改变
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.49,0:19:25.37,Default,,0,0,0,,才参选了班长
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.25,0:19:27.33,Default,,0,0,0,,可是结果
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.27,0:19:30.93,Default,,0,0,0,,副班长
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.41,0:19:33.53,Default,,0,0,0,,又是微妙的…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.00,0:19:35.81,Default,,0,0,0,,还有 为什么在铁棒上
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.36,0:19:38.23,Default,,0,0,0,,刚才也在说我的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.37,0:19:40.56,Default,,0,0,0,,说我那么残念
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.78,0:19:41.54,Default,,0,0,0,,那是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.54,0:19:42.60,Default,,0,0,0,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.71,0:19:46.06,Default,,0,0,0,,是在说想和本庄同学交朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.49,0:19:47.82,Default,,0,0,0,,难以置信
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.10,0:19:50.32,Default,,0,0,0,,居然想和残念衣架的我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.12,0:19:54.36,Default,,0,0,0,,本庄同学才不残念
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.22,0:19:59.92,Default,,0,0,0,,多亏了本庄同学 我才能和菜子和好的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.56,0:20:01.29,Default,,0,0,0,,而且
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.88,0:20:04.23,Default,,0,0,0,,那么体贴 那么可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.53,0:20:05.52,Default,,0,0,0,,可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.71,0:20:10.66,Default,,0,0,0,,帮帮我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.08,0:20:16.35,Default,,0,0,0,,脸算是可爱的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.64,0:20:17.06,Default,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.44,0:20:19.22,Default,,0,0,0,,你们干什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.48,0:20:22.24,Default,,0,0,0,,抓住残念衣架的我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.73,0:20:24.77,Default,,0,0,0,,现在还说这些
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.20,0:20:26.26,Default,,0,0,0,,我才没有
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.53,0:20:30.39,Default,,0,0,0,,我才没有开心呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.28,0:20:35.92,Default,,0,0,0,,她说不开心
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.07,0:20:38.01,Default,,0,0,0,,差一点了 加油
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.63,0:20:46.23,Default,,0,0,0,,能做朋友吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.90,0:20:50.81,Default,,0,0,0,,那是因为要和全班都做朋友的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.38,0:20:52.89,Default,,0,0,0,,那也是原因之一
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.94,0:20:56.00,Default,,0,0,0,,可是 就算没有这个
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.44,0:21:00.04,Default,,0,0,0,,我也想和本庄同学交朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.63,0:21:09.39,Default,,0,0,0,,不行吗 朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.45,0:21:14.85,Default,,0,0,0,,她说不行
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.85,0:21:17.24,Default,,0,0,0,,不是的 刚才是肯定
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.34,0:21:19.12,Default,,0,0,0,,意思是能做朋友的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.09,0:21:28.82,Default,,0,0,0,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.43,0:21:32.15,Default,,0,0,0,,请多关照哦 一里同学
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.59,0:21:34.59,Default,,0,0,0,,本庄同学
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.61,0:21:43.71,Default,,0,0,0,,太高兴了就会昏迷的 这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.98,0:21:45.38,Default,,0,0,0,,你能来扶一下吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.00,0:21:50.41,Default,,0,0,0,,在那之前 有件事要跟砂尾同学说
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.65,0:21:52.40,Default,,0,0,0,,这是你的包
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.70,0:21:55.30,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.85,0:21:57.05,Default,,0,0,0,,要说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.03,0:22:07.94,Default,,0,0,0,,不要用「你」称呼我
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.05,0:22:09.60,Default,,0,0,0,,不要用「你」称呼我
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.67,0:22:11.89,Default,,0,0,0,,不要用「你」称呼我
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.54,0:22:13.70,Default,,0,0,0,,自尊心那么强
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.78,0:22:14.62,Default,,0,0,0,,明明那么残念
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.69,0:22:16.20,Default,,0,0,0,,不要说我残念
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.24,0:22:16.97,Default,,0,0,0,,很残念
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.97,0:22:17.93,Default,,0,0,0,,不要说
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.93,0:22:18.56,Default,,0,0,0,,残念
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.56,0:22:20.09,Default,,0,0,0,,不要说
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.60,0:22:21.53,Default,,0,0,0,,太好了
